        <content>
          <p>Whilst reductions in income are concentrated around low-tariff and specialist (other) providers, there is significant variation within tariff groupings. Furthermore, providers of foundation years vary year-on-year, with five providers in academic year 2021/22 not admitting entrants for impacted courses in academic year 2022/23. Therefore, the overall impact to total income for providers listed within Table 4 is unlikely to capture the variation in impact at a provider level. </p>
        </content>
