      <level>
        <content>
          <p>All OfS registered HE providers, excluding Further Education Colleges (FECs), are required to submit data on academic staff to HESA. However, the return of data on non-academic staff became voluntary submission from academic year 2019/20 onwards. Given that not all HE providers reported their non-academic staff numbers for academic year 2022/23, we have calculated a ratio of academic/non-academic staff in academic year 2018/19 (when the data was last complete) to estimate non-academic staff numbers for providers which did not provide complete data for academic year 2022/23.</p>
