        <content>
          <p>Analysis of SLC data on student loan borrowers and outlay which provide insights into the impact of policy changes on the number of students taking out a loan and any impacts to the Exchequer.  Our modelling assumptions have been outlined within this IA and can be tested against final outcomes post academic year 2025/26.</p>
